    • collectQuarterData

      private final void collectQuarterData(Map<String,String> contents, int quarter) throws IOException, SQLException
      Collects the data for one quarter.
      Parameters:
      contents - The target for the collected data.
      quarter - The number of the quarter to process. 0 is the current quarter, -1 is the last quarter before the current, and so on.
      Throws:
      IOException - A problem occurred when creating the chart.
      SQLException - A problem was encountered when retrieving the data from the database.
